Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.17,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.34,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.85,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.68,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.14,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:51.52,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:56.95,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:03.49,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:08.67,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:14.55,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:20.64,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.17,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}逐渐淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.34,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你的面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.85,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}害怕这逐渐的  忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.68,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.14,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想把这份风景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:51.52,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}锁进我的心里  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:56.95,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想与你相见这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:03.49,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}却很需要勇气  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:08.67,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:14.55,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明天当我  睁开眼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:20.64,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你能在我身旁而已
